Messaging App in Typescript

Main Objectives
    - Learn Typescript
    - Cleaner folder structure than previous projects

-- apps
--- frontend
----- public
----- src
----- vite.config.ts
--- backend
----- prisma
----- src/
----- tsconfig.json
-- packages
----- ui 
----- utils
----- types
-- gitignore
-- package.json

Project reqs
-------------
- Authorization (JWT, stored somewhere other than LocalStorage)
- Ability to open chat and send messages to other users 
- Ability to customise profile and view others profiles

Backend models
-------------
- Users (id, username, pw, bio, profile picture, date of birth, sentMessages)
- Messages (recipientID, senderID, message, time)

Frontend pages
-------------
- Homepage
- Login / Signup
- Messages
- Profile






